Germany’s Seibert Denies Report EU Is Holding Talks on Greece Leaving Euro

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-05-06T16:19:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/germany-s-seibert-denies-report-eu-is-holding-talks-on-greece-leaving-euro.html
Greece ’s possible exit from the euro
area isn’t being discussed in the European Union, said Steffen Seibert, German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s chief spokesman.
“This isn’t on the table and hasn’t been on the table for the
German government and isn’t a topic at the European level,” he
said by telephone today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
